data.title: Stephen V of Hungary and Croatia "Štefan V" ÁRPÁD(házi) King (1239
data.meta_description: V. István - Stephen V of Hungary and Croatia ÁRPÁD(házi) was born on October 18, 1239 in Buda, Pest, Hungary, son of IV. Béla of Hungary ÁRPÁD(házi) and Maria Lascarina. He was married about June 1255 to Erzsébet of Cumenia, they gave birth to 1 child. He died on August  6, 1272 in Csepel sziget / Island, Hungary. This information is part of Family tree Homs by George Homs on Genealogy Online.
